snippet.title: VOIN - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A single developer has created VOIN, a new first-person dark-fantasy action-RPG with violent combat and high-speed traversal. A representative described it to IGN as "DOOM, Diablo, and Neon White having a baby at a goth rave party." A public playtest is happening on March 8. 

If you're interested, you can wishlist it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2464530/VOIN/

#IGN #Gaming #VOIN
